Currently the contentbylabel macro can be used on a page to show pages for a personal label (i.e. {contentbylabel:my:favourite} will show the favourites of the user *visiting that page*). I would like to be able to add labels to a page and use the contentbylabel macro to list the ones that I have added I would suggest syntax:

{contentbylabel:thelabel|user=stafford.vaughan}

to show all pages that are labelled with "thelabel" for the user stafford.vaughan.

Thanks,
Stafford

